        "headline": "Beach Hazards Statement issued June 7 at 6:49PM CDT until June 8 at 7:00PM CDT by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI",
        "description": "* WHAT...Life threatening waves of 3 to 5 feet and dangerous\ncurrents are expected.\n\n* WHERE...Sheboygan, Ozaukee, Milwaukee and Racine Counties.\n\n* WHEN...From midnight CDT tonight through Monday evening.\n\n* IMPACTS...Dangerous swimming conditions are expected due to\nhigh waves and onshore winds.",
